{"tid":393203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行政會議成員湯家驊：我不認識蔡若蓮 ... 但看了這張照片，我痛心疾首！","createTime":"2017-09-09T05:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T12:16:29.000Z","uid":11001,"like":3,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74479bac58ce9fc9806d85e4834f7eb697883549","tid":393203,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:27:12.000Z","msg":"我不認識蔡若蓮，也不知她曾經做過什麼十惡不赦、殺人放火的錯事，但看了這張照片，我痛心疾首！這是教大學生在所謂「民主牆」上的大字報。寫的人將會是我們下一代的為人師表、相信也自認是民主派支持者。為何我們的社會、我們的教育制度竟然淪落至此？為何心向民主的人，意然變得這樣邪惡？假如民主派不公開譴責這種惡毒言行、勸止盲目仇恨的漫延，民主運動尚有什麼希望？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/211789612184052/photos/1820116881351309/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F211789612184052%2Fphotos%2F1820116881351309%2F&d=r7mmPrYMUcWEMID77SUNezCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c70e6df8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/211789612184052/photos/1820116881351309/</a>"},{"pid":"69bbe069190243ad76060edd829504b5fb2a430d","tid":393203,"uid":16447,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:28:15.000Z","msg":"也不知她曾經做過什麼十惡不赦、殺人放火的錯事<br />\n<br />\n佢做議員係咪訓足咁多年"},{"pid":"6e94170770498aea93bdc61030dfbe999d472500","tid":393203,"uid":59976,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:29:00.000Z","msg":"又要淚灑雪廠街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e117eacb473300283999a201d89375b4422659","tid":393203,"uid":19557,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"佢就算喇 淚灑雨廠街 <br />\n我勸大家留個負皮 上一頁就算"},{"pid":"d69a1d32a0e0bae9079019c1651e2d628316bd52","tid":393203,"uid":7840,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:29:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f17d99919528e26e56eed5c96a0fb2ffea24297","tid":393203,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquot