blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/891141/湯家驊%3A普選夢再落空+香港黑暗一天</a><br />\n31-8-2014<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊指出，人大常委會今日的決定令人痛心，是香港黑暗的一天。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/article.php?catalias=ronnytong&amp;id=26407&amp;secalias=archive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Farticle.php%3Fcatalias%3Dronnytong%26id%3D26407%26secalias%3Darchive&d=r7mmPrYMUcWEMID77SUNezCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e0907952\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/article.php?catalias=ronnytong&amp;id=26407&amp;secalias=archive</a><br />\n24-7-2014<br />\n機上298人全數罹難，令國際社會震驚。如此令人痛心疾首的空難為何會發生？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://rkwtong.blogspot.hk/2009/11/blog-post_27.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frkwtong.blogspot.hk%2F2009%2F11%2Fblog-post_27.html%3Fm%3D1&d=r7mmPrYMUcWEMID77SUNezCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9fd5c195\" target=\"_blank\">http://rkwtong.blogspot.hk/2009/11/blog-post_27.html?m=1</a><br />\n27-11-2009<br />\n這是導致整個民主運動裂痕日深的催化劑，也可能是瓦解民主運動的先兆。中央二十年做不到的，我們可能在短短四個月間做到了；能不令人痛心疾首？"},{"pid":"0157d6d84abcf3ce6e809cd8b97d641dd8d3f53a","tid":393203,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">湯先生每隔一排就痛心，要唔要去醫院做返個body check好啲？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/48746/-宣誓風波-湯家驊指誓詞冒犯涉道德倫理問題-感痛心疾首\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F48746%2F-%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E6%8C%87%E8%AA%93%E8%A9%9E%E5%86%92%E7%8A%AF%E6%B6%89%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E5%80%AB%E7%90%86%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-%E6%84%9F%E7%97%9B%E5%BF%83%E7%96%BE%E9%A6%96&d=r7mmPrYMUcWEMID77SUNezCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=97eb4ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/48746/-宣誓風波-湯家驊指誓詞冒犯涉道德倫理問題-感痛心疾首</a><br />\n16-10-2016<br />\n湯家驊指誓詞冒犯涉道德倫理問題　感